            perferendis earum nam porro architecto cupiditate voluptates
            consectetur sapiente? Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur
            adipisicing elit. Distinctio fugiat quam similique.
          </p>

          <a
            href="/about"
            class="font-bold mb-4 mt-2 text-lg flex text-purple-500 underline-offset-4 underline py-0"
            >Read More
          </a>

          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <h2 class="font-bold !text-xl sm:text-inherit">
              OKAKE, IFEOMA CHINWE
            </h2>
            <small>Director/Founder</small>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials -->

    <section class="bg-purple-100 sm:py-24 py-12 px-6 sm:px-0">
      <div class="container mb-16 flex justify-between items-end">
        <AboutSection
